36:03.371 --> 36:05.206
- Fucker.
- All right, you go to bed.

36:05.206 --> 36:07.208
I'll be right back.

36:07.208 --> 36:10.252
He's just under a lot
of stress now, okay?

36:10.252 --> 36:14.298
