44:56.820 --> 44:58.446
Ow! Hey!

44:58.446 --> 45:00.532
You asked!

45:00.532 --> 45:03.744
V...

45:03.744 --> 45:06.996
Oh, V, honey.

45:06.996 --> 45:08.248
Go away, Kevin.

45:08.248 --> 45:10.792
- Oh, come on.
[babies crying]

45:10.792 --> 45:12.627
Go away.

45:12.627 --> 45:15.004
I don't want you
to dress like anybody else.

45:15.004 --> 45:19.175
I want you to dress like you--
Veronica clothes.

45:19.175 --> 45:22.805
Babies, Kev--
you better go and hold 'em.

45:22.805 --> 45:26.683
[crying continues]

45:26.683 --> 45:28.768
Babies, Kev!

45:28.768 --> 45:31.980
[crying continues]

45:31.980 --> 45:34.107
