before they die!

45:37.819 --> 45:41.072
No, I want to be here
with you.

45:41.072 --> 45:43.575
Go get the babies!

45:43.575 --> 45:47.745
[crying continues]

45:47.745 --> 45:49.747
Kevin.

45:54.544 --> 45:56.964
We'll go do it
together, okay?

45:56.964 --> 46:01.885
[crying continues]

46:01.885 --> 46:05.221
Oh, shit, they sure
can scream, can't they?

46:05.221 --> 46:08.224
[tender music]

46:08.224 --> 46:16.274
♪ ♪

46:53.436 --> 46:55.897
