52:26.310 --> 52:28.312
Grow up, Fiona.

52:33.985 --> 52:36.988
[cell phone vibrating]

52:40.783 --> 52:42.785
[grunts]
Fuck.

52:42.785 --> 52:44.161
Hello?

52:44.161 --> 52:45.329
Hello?

52:49.750 --> 52:53.087
[line trilling]

52:55.339 --> 52:57.550
