of each other.

53:58.736 --> 54:01.030
I don't want you
sitting around,

54:01.030 --> 54:02.907
worrying, watching me,

54:02.907 --> 54:05.701
waiting for me to do
my next crazy shit.

54:05.701 --> 54:07.203
It means thick and thin,

54:07.203 --> 54:09.246
good times, bad, sickness,
health, all that shit.

54:09.246 --> 54:10.915
You gonna marry me?

54:10.915 --> 54:12.625
Are we gonna go down
to the courthouse in some tuxes

54:12.625 --> 54:14.377
