54:14.377 --> 54:16.003
Fuck you.

54:16.003 --> 54:19.298
No, thanks.
I've already done that.

54:19.298 --> 54:21.343
What the hell
is wrong with you?

54:21.343 --> 54:23.386
Too much!

54:25.346 --> 54:27.598
Too much is wrong with me.

54:27.598 --> 54:30.559
That's the problem,
isn't it?

54:30.559 --> 54:32.228
Too much is wrong with me,

54:32.228 --> 54:33.979
and you can't do
anything about that.

54:33.979 --> 54:35.606
You can't change it.

54:35.606 --> 54:38.025
